sentences: Following this, she moved to the West Coast to drum for Team Dresch in 1993.
When Team Dresch broke up in 1998, York and band-mate Kaia Wilson, together with Alison Martlew, formed the power punk lesbian-feminist band, The Butchies (1998-2005), which put out four albums.
